!=======================================================================
! Input file for inflow-outflow boundary layer code
!

18000	nsteps      number of time steps to run
0.      timeLimit   stopping time (0.=ignore)
48.     whours      wall hours (for SGI only; should be <= time in rundefs)
1		iprint      interval to print out diagnostic information
1		ipout       interval to print out restart file (might be same as iprint????)
0		istat       Calculate statistics?  Sampling interval

1.70 	Re          Reynolds number !!!!!!!!!!!!slide=2
1       iSGS        Use a subgrid-scale model?

! Time-step control
0			iCFL        Run at (1) constant CFL number   (0) constant dt
1.0			CFLlimit    maximum allowable CFL number
! 1			flag_newdt  Changed time step?
0.25		dt          time step

! Inflow generation
0      inflow      Type of inflow: (0)laminar (1)data file
0      inflowFluct (0)none (1)random (2)OS disc. (3)OS cont. (4)FST (5)2D+3D (6)multiple OS cont
1.     ubulk        bulk velocity for laminar inflow

! Boundary condition for each face
1      BC_bottom   Type of boundary condition: (0)free slip (1)no slip (2) periodic (3) sliding
3      BC_top      Type of boundary condition: (0)free slip (1)no slip (2) periodic (3) sliding
2      BC_left     Type of boundary condition: (1)prescribed-inflow    (2) periodic
2      BC_right    Type of boundary condition: (1)convective-outflow   (2) periodic
2      BC_back     Type of boundary condition: (0)free slip (1)no slip (2) periodic
2      BC_front    Type of boundary condition: (0)free slip (1)no slip (2) periodic

!Sliding velocity
0.		uwall_b	   u sliding velocity of bottom wall
2.0		uwall_t	   u sliding velocity of top wall
0.		vwall_b    v sliding velocity of bottom wall
0.		vwall_t	   v sliding velocity of top wall
0.		wwall_b    w sliding velocity of bottom wall
0.		wwall_t	   w sliding velocity of top wall

! Free-stream turbulence parameters
0.03	Tu	Turbulence intensity at inlet
32	nw	Number of frequency modes
32	nKy	Number of modes wall-normal direction
32	nKz	Number of modes in spanwise direction
1.3	kp	Peak of inlet energy spectrum

! Animation
12        ianim
7.5     save_dt

! Quick parameters
0.00       x_QUICK       Pre-multiply the Quadratic Upstream Interpolation by (x_QUICK)

! Poisson solver - multigrid parameter
1        idct	     Option for Direct Cosine Transform in x: (0)multigrid  (1)dctx
3        ngrid       Number of grid levels
5        ncycle      Number of V-cycles through grid levels
2        npre        Number of pre-iterations/relaxations at each level 
100      nitmax      Maximum number of iterations
500      nitmaxb     Maximum number of iterations at base level
1.e-12   resmin      Minimum residual
1.e-12   resminb     Minimum residual at base level
1.0      omegak1     Relaxation parameter for multigrid solver
1.0      omegakn     Relaxation parameter for multigrid solver

! More stuff for Xiahua's code
4        iprob       (4) turbine blade 
2        ipoisson    NOT USED
0        iread_avt   Read average data?

!TJ: Pressure gradient
0 	iPrj	 	(0)fixed dpdx (1)fixed mdot 
0.0	GPxi     	Fixed pressure gradient (time average from fixed mdot code, in terms of a FLUX. Hardwire if you want)

